The paper deals with video stream switching and compression, which are topics related to multimedia (cs.MM) and information theory (cs.IT). The use of merge mechanisms and coding techniques also suggests a connection to computer vision (cs.CV) and networking (cs.NI). Finally, the optimization of rate-distortion criteria involves signal processing (cs.SI).
